Company Overview of MOCON, Inc., Vaculok Product Line



Snapshot People




Company Overview
MOCON, Inc., Vaculok Product Line, manufactures Vacuum Insulated Panels (VIPs) under the brand name Vaculok. The panels provide temperature protection packaging. MOCON is based in Minneapolis, Minnesota.


Minneapolis, MN 55428United States










