MOCON, Inc. - Baseline manufactures custom gas analyzers and detectors for toxic gas detection, environmental monitoring, mud logging hydrocarbons during oil and gas exploration, specialty and beverage gas analysis. MOCON - Baseline also produces the award winning piD-TECH® series of photoionization sensors.





 
